snippet.title: EXCLUSIVE: 'Nothing could have prepared me for 2020' - Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Actress Amber Heard talks exclusively to Sky News about her new TV series - in a year where Johnny Depp's libel case dominated her year.

'The Stand' - which was made before coronavirus existed - is about a flu which kills 99% of the population.

Filming on the show was completed in March, just before the pandemic took hold across the world.

Read more here:
https://news.sky.com/story/amber-heard-nothing-could-have-prepared-me-for-2020-12164247
